/** * Return the name of the persistence unit used to create this * EntityManagerFactory, or {@code null} if it is an unnamed default. *

If {@code getPersistenceUnitInfo()} returns non-null, the result of * {@code getPersistenceUnitName()} must be equal to the value returned by * {@code PersistenceUnitInfo.getPersistenceUnitName()}. * @see #getPersistenceUnitInfo() * @see javax.persistence.spi.PersistenceUnitInfo#getPersistenceUnitName() */

/** * Return the name of the persistence unit used to create this * EntityManagerFactory, or {@code null} if it is an unnamed default. *

If {@code getPersistenceUnitInfo()} returns non-null, the result of * {@code getPersistenceUnitName()} must be equal to the value returned by * {@code PersistenceUnitInfo.getPersistenceUnitName()}. * @see #getPersistenceUnitInfo() * @see javax.persistence.spi.PersistenceUnitInfo#getPersistenceUnitName() */ @Nullable String getPersistenceUnitName().

code: /**  * Return the JDBC DataSource that this EntityManagerFactory  * obtains its JDBC Connections from.  * @return the JDBC DataSource, or {@code null} if not known  */ @Nullable DataSource getDataSource().
